":224173,"uid":42764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T18:18:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>文言文先正 DSE中文攞分位<br />\n只需你直譯 ＋ 解文意<br />\n睇得多自然識<br />\n好多都係用故事形式去講<br />\n有少少對儒墨道既認識都大致搞掂DSE中文<br />\n<br />\n利申：閱讀5**</blockquote><br />\n咁就代表合理要讀???<br />\n中文科霸佔大量學習時數，減少其他課程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80057ac50ae90255dd2f64b5df659ace97a9850a","tid":224173,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T00:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24faed0e950336414c399f1eb4aacc87a4fe5bc8","tid":224173,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T00:46:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中文系表示當時有個教授講<br />\n中文唔係會計果種技能科<br />\n而係學修養的科，基本上一個中文好的學者修養脾氣都好好。<br />\n同文字的力量可以比槍更強<br />\n好似中國人文革就將班文人做官方喉舌<br />\n叫工農文藝兵<br />\n不停寫d 幫政權打j文章，去宣揚政權<br />\n之後再用班文人去幫政權掩飾<br />\n<br />\n再就近代睇，華文文學搵錢都好大<br />\n怪獸與他們的產地的怪獸根本就係山海經出來<br />\n龍珠悟空由西遊記來<br />\n六國論可以應用呢家香港形勢</blockquote><br />\n中文=/=中文科"},{"pid":"ff2abab9c1e24006a858d969dc52c564ffbedec7","tid":224173,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:24:28.000Z","msg":"考試前一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2087b8fdfae8ba4596b31c31ee0b33d4df8c13","tid":224173,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T11:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c28daab3c7a25ed87b459269870930e2c49c59","tid":224173,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da5d25160f1341798e2514ebd4149e02e5790718","tid":224173,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:27:01.000Z","msg":"之後就話大陸學生好勁<br />\n香港學生畢業全部做低下階層<br />\n高層全部大陸狗"},{"pid":"233a1